"The Royal Family's Secret Recipe #1\n"
"The Princess's Favorite: <1.se_co>Fruitcake<2.re_co>\n"
"\n"
"Boil any two (or more) pieces of fruit\n"
"with Tabantha wheat and cane sugar\n"
"for a good while.\n"
"Eating this dish will apparently clear your\n"
"head and help you focus on things such\n"
"as ancient technology research."
msgstr ""

